cross: Cattleya Irene Finney (1964) x Cattleya Sierra Doll

measurements.description: Three flat flowers on one inflorescence, two buds on one immature inflorescence; sepals cream overlaid lavender; petals cream overlaid lavender, veined darker distally, upper margins ruffled; lip ruffled, cream overlaid lavender, blotched yellow centrally, darker lavender striations distal tip; column light lavender, anther cap white; substance firm; texture diamond dust.
